title: Molecularly engineered potential of d-orbital modulated iron-bridged delaminated MBene for rechargeable Zn–air batteries
content:
Energy Environ. Sci., 2024, 17,6559-6570
DOI: 10.1039/D4EE02868F, Paper
Seung Woong Nam, Thanh Hai Nguyen, Duy Thanh Tran, Van An Dinh, Thi Thuy Nga Ta, Chung-Li Dong, Nam Hoon Kim, Joong Hee Lee
An air cathode with high catalytic activity and reversibility toward the OER and ORR is designed by the typical coordinations of iron phthalocyanine molecule crystals on delaminated MoAl1−xB MBene sheets.
